commit.message:
sparc.md (negtf2_notv9 split): Give NEG SFmode.

	* config/sparc/sparc.md (negtf2_notv9 split): Give NEG
	SFmode.
	(negsf2): Fix insn output string.

 	making note of this dependency existing in sparc.c
